name: Samusky
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Solana's First Staking Available Meme Token

We believe meme tokens are the future. Samusky will be an extensible project, not just a meme. Staking Soon!

The first step is staking, then an easy-to-use DEX and then AMM.
